			shape: "heart"
			subtitle: "Terrari-oh..wrong game?: The Terra Blade is a legendary weapon which will launch mana from the user's inventory to create powerful projectiles that will deal lots of damage to their enemies. To launch bursts, just left-click with the TerraBlade in hand. This sword will also repair itself using mana from the player's inventory"
