			subtitle: "Its large. Left Click for more info"
			description: [
				"The Cleaver is a sword-like weapon made with two tough tool rods, a large plate, and a large sword blade. They swing very slowly due to the massive size, giving you Mining Fatigue III, but do more damage than most other weapons. They have the natural ability to sometimes decapitate mobs(beheading) , leaving their heads as an item drop to wear, or to use as a decoration. This works on zombies, creepers, skeletons, wither skeletons and other players."
				""
				"Keep in mind that this quest is here just to let you know that this tool exists and that you can make it. Finishing this quest doesn't actually mean you did what you had to."
